#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/index.rst:2
#: a93b51a1a3994a0383a1f02105d0280c
msgid "Fluid Mechanics"
msgstr "流体力学"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/index.rst:4
#: 41a64bed455d45329b3d9dc368b47022
msgid ""
"A family of worked Navier-Stokes examples in ``examples/fluid/``, from the "
"lid-driven cavity benchmark (2D and 3D) to a Rayleigh-Bénard convection "
"problem coupling momentum and energy. They all share the same underlying "
"recipe — a custom ``NavierStokesAssembler`` (or its transient cousin) "
"defined in the example file, SUPG/PSPG stabilization for equal-order P1-P1 "
"elements, Picard linearization for steady solves, implicit Euler for "
"transient ones — so once you have read :doc:`cavity` the rest are "
"essentially geometry and boundary-condition variations."
msgstr ""
"``examples/fluid/`` 中收录了一系列完整的纳维-斯托克斯算例，从顶盖驱动方腔基准（2D 与 3D）到耦合动量与能量的瑞利-"
"贝纳德对流问题。它们都共享同一套底层方案——在算例文件中定义的自定义 ``NavierStokesAssembler``\\ （或其瞬态版本）、用于等阶"
" P1-P1 单元的 SUPG/PSPG 稳定化、稳态求解的 Picard 线性化、瞬态求解的隐式欧拉法——因此一旦你读过 "
":doc:`cavity`\\ ，其余算例本质上只是几何和边界条件上的变体。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/index.rst:14
#: f5ee60ca229a4661acd7db111c029fad
msgid ""
"The ``NavierStokesAssembler`` itself lives **in the example folder**, not in"
" ``tensormesh.assemble``. It is intentionally example-grade: the production-"
"quality version will move into the core library when the assembler API for "
"vector-valued problems stabilizes."
msgstr ""
"``NavierStokesAssembler`` 本身位于\\ **算例文件夹中**\\ ，而不在 ``tensormesh.assemble`` "
"里。这是有意为之的示例级实现：当面向向量值问题的装配器 API 稳定后，生产级版本将会迁入核心库。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/index.rst:23
#: 9287bc072a8445da98678e82068a7a03
msgid "Lid-Driven Cavity"
msgstr "顶盖驱动方腔"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/index.rst:28
#: 3f3f7f14f6d8411181ecec8a9f162b88
msgid ""
"Steady NS at Re=100, SUPG/PSPG stabilization, Picard iteration — in 2D and "
"3D with one dimension-generic assembler."
msgstr "Re=100 的稳态纳维-斯托克斯，SUPG/PSPG 稳定化，Picard 迭代——用同一个维度通用的装配器同时处理 2D 与 3D。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/index.rst:31
#: 689170ec077640f68af8870d0a478f60
msgid "Cylinder Flow (Vortex Shedding)"
msgstr "圆柱绕流（涡脱落）"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/index.rst:36
#: dfc5e8c2efa845dd906953d0bef16cd7
msgid ""
"Transient DFG benchmark, implicit Euler, drag/lift/Strouhal post-processing."
msgstr "瞬态 DFG 基准，隐式欧拉法，阻力/升力/斯特劳哈尔数的后处理。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/index.rst:38
#: 759d6a803f48404c9002199be8b7326e
msgid "Flow Past Multiple Obstacles"
msgstr "绕多个障碍物的流动"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/index.rst:43
#: 79c67bce473d40eeb579fa5bd94251a9
msgid ""
"Steady channel flow at Re=150 around six circular obstacles via MeshGen CSG."
msgstr "Re=150 的稳态通道流，绕六个圆形障碍物，网格通过 MeshGen 的 CSG 构造。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/index.rst:45
#: 84946935c07748e28ff9ebde68a0c604
msgid "Rayleigh-Bénard Convection"
msgstr "瑞利-贝纳德对流"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/index.rst:50
#: 351b577a450740f19096f222d956e2e5
msgid "Boussinesq-coupled momentum + heat transport, buoyancy-driven flow."
msgstr "布西内斯克近似耦合动量与热输运，浮力驱动的流动。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/index.rst:52
#: 97287f70ecd64d36aed640726dc45ac7
msgid "Taylor-Green Vortex"
msgstr "泰勒-格林涡"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/index.rst:57
#: 82705f00dea445d292494e24ccdfa13b
msgid "Decaying vortex with exact solution — the convergence-study showcase."
msgstr "具有精确解的衰减涡——收敛性研究的范例。"

